---
title: Pork Schnitzel Fingers with Parmesan Coleslaw and Green Beans
description: Crispy pork schnitzel fingers are fun to make – and even more fun to eat! We’ve paired it with a fresh crunchy Parmesan coleslaw that’s dressed to impress.
